## üîó SIDEBAR NAVIGATION - HOW TO ADD NEW LINK

Edit `components/layout/Sidebar.tsx`:

```tsx
// 1. IMPORT THE ICON
import { 
  FiHome, 
  FiDroplet, 
  FiSmartphone,
  FiYourNewIcon  // ‚Üê ADD YOUR ICON HERE
} from 'react-icons/fi';

// 2. ADD TO navItems ARRAY
const navItems: NavItem[] = [
  {
    name: 'Dashboard',
    path: '/dashboard',
    icon: <FiHome size={20} />,
    color: '#c5e6ff' // Light blue
  },
  {
    name: 'CSS Themes',
    path: '/dashboard/themes',
    icon: <FiDroplet size={20} />,
    color: '#d2b7ff' // Light purple
  },
  {
    name: 'Button Gallery',
    path: '/dashboard/buttons',
    icon: <FiSmartphone size={20} />,
    color: '#ffb7c5' // Pink
  },
  // 3. ADD YOUR NEW LINK
  {
    name: 'Your New Section',
    path: '/dashboard/your-section', // ‚Üê CREATE THIS PAGE
    icon: <FiYourNewIcon size={20} />,
    color: '#b7ffca' // Light green - choose from palette
  }
];
```

**COLOR ASSIGNMENT RULES FOR SIDEBAR:**
- Dashboard: `#c5e6ff` (Light Blue)
- CSS Themes: `#d2b7ff` (Light Purple)  
- Button Gallery: `#ffb7c5` (Pink)
- Next Section: `#b7ffca` (Light Green)
- Next: Cycle through remaining colors

