```
RootLayout (app/layout.tsx)
    ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ DashboardLayout (components/layout/DashboardLayout.tsx)
        ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Sidebar (components/layout/Sidebar.tsx)
