            ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Header with Icon
            ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Optional: CategoryFilter
            ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Optional: CodeTypeToggle
            ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Grid of Cards
            ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Card Component with Copy Functionality
            ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Pagination
```

